name: The Hungry Spider
description:
This spider is the first creature from my first set of cards related to purgatorial monsters.

It's card number 1 of the purgatorial monsters collection.
 The spider is the most hungry one among the spiders in history, it has eaten billions of living beings, and it is still Hungry.  Can you take care of this spider?  Do not worry, This spider is currently imprisoned in this purgatorial card and cannot harm anyone!
